"Alberto Campo Baeza graduated in architecture at E.T.S. Arquitectura de Madrid in 1971. His works and projects have been widely published in international magazines, shown at major exhibitions and awarded with numerous prizes. He is currently professor at University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia.
